We did it! 1 MILLION orders and counting! 🎉

A huge THANK YOU to all our amazing customers for making this journey unforgettable. As a proud brand from the North East, we’ve faced roadblocks along the way, but we’re committed to solving them and providing a smooth experience for you all. Our goal is to create a perfect, no-wastage, no-inventory sustainable model — doing our bit for the environment, one box at a time.

We’re just getting started, and we couldn’t have reached this milestone without your love and support. Keep the orders coming – we’re ready for more!
